flowchart LR
  CSV[CSV point list] --> VBS[WinCC VBScript]
  VBS --> HMI[HMI / PC Runtime]
  HMI <--> PLC[S7-1200 PLC]
  PLC --> IF[Opto-isolated I/O]
  IF --> XY[X/Y drives]
  IF --> Z[Z actuator]
  IF --> STEP[Stepper plunger]
  ENC[Incremental encoders] --> PLC
  SENS[Zero/end/process sensors] --> PLC
  CSV --> MATLAB[MATLAB offline analysis]
